      "Ms. Buolamwini, who spent hours prepping the 60-minutes team, was summarily not given credit for her work, nor was she acknowledged as the one who made the work groundbreaking; thus erasing her from the narration while her work and knowledge were credited to what she refers to as 'Pale Males.'",
      "Appalled, I reshared a LinkedIn by The Algorithmic Justice League as well as one by Ms. Buolamwini herself on my personal LinkedIn profile with the following comment hoping to inform others of how Black women continue to be treated as disposable within the tech community: <em>'Pay attention: this is what misogynoir looks and feels like.'</em>",
